{"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ ("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setReverseProxy:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"NSString","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"url","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"headers:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"NSDictionary<NSString *,NSString *>","preciseIdentifier":"c:Q$objc(cs)NSDictionary","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"headers"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"url","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The full URL of your reverse proxy endpoint (e.g., “https:\/\/proxy.company.com\/pushwoosh”). Must not be nil or empty."}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Optional dictionary of custom HTTP headers. Pass nil if no custom headers are needed.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"headers"}]},{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Routes all Pushwoosh SDK network requests through your own proxy server.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"This is useful for:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Enterprise security","type":"text"}]},{"text":": Route traffic through corporate proxies","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Regional compliance"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": Ensure data flows through specific regions","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Network monitoring","type":"text"}]},{"text":": Inspect and log SDK traffic","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Firewall restrictions","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Work around corporate firewall rules"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The proxy must forward requests to the appropriate Pushwoosh API endpoints"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"while preserving all headers and request body content."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Settings are not persisted and must be set on every app start."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"URL must start with https:\/\/ or http:\/\/."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Custom headers are only applied when reverse proxy is active.","type":"text"}]},{"level":2,"text":"Example","type":"heading","anchor":"Example"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Configure proxy for enterprise deployment:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["class NetworkConfiguration {","","    func configureForEnterprise() {","        guard let proxyURL = Configuration.shared.pushwooshProxyURL else {","            return","        }","","        Pushwoosh.configure.setReverseProxy(proxyURL, headers: nil)","","        Logger.info(\"Pushwoosh configured to use proxy: \\(proxyURL)\")","    }","","    func configureForRegion(_ region: Region) {","        switch region {","        case .eu:","            Pushwoosh.configure.setReverseProxy(","                \"https:\/\/eu-proxy.company.com\/pushwoosh\",","                headers: [\"X-Auth-Token\": \"your-token\"]","            )","        case .asia:","            Pushwoosh.configure.setReverseProxy(","                \"https:\/\/asia-proxy.company.com\/pushwoosh\",","                headers: nil","            )","        case .us:","            break \/\/ No proxy needed","        }","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing"}],"kind":"content"}],"sections":[],"abstract":[{"text":"Sets a reverse proxy URL and optional custom HTTP headers for all SDK network requests.","type":"text"}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setreverseproxy:headers:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Type Method","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)setReverseProxy:headers:","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"symbolKind":"method","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setReverseProxy:headers:"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setReverseProxy:headers:","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"setReverseProxy:headers:","role":"symbol"},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setReverseProxy:headers:"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/setReverseProxy:headers:":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets a reverse proxy URL and optional custom HTTP headers for all SDK network requests."}],"fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setReverseProxy:headers:"}],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setreverseproxy:headers:","kind":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setReverseProxy:headers:","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setReverseProxy:headers:","title":"setReverseProxy:headers:","role":"symbol"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","kind":"symbol","role":"collection","title":"PushwooshCore","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}]},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"abstract":[],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"PWConfiguration"}],"title":"PWConfiguration","type":"topic","role":"symbol"}}}